reviews.review_text:
Celtics on stage! Those who know me know that I'm not the world's biggest 80's fan, 
however I recall really enjoying this show.

There was an energy level and spirit that was high compared to many of the other '85 shows I caught.

There were a bunch of really tall guys on stage that night. Bill Walton, Larry Bird, Kevin McHale, and Danny Ainge!

Best sound for my taste I find this the best sounding source. I find the Nak 100 pull to be a bit bright sounding for my taste. It's not perfect, but I like the warmth in this recording. Oh, and set 2 fit's on 1 cd.
